Class ImageCanvas

  • java.lang.Object
    • ImageCanvas
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ImageCanvas
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to distribute images over the network. It implements the Serializable Iface and has a single transient member variable that holds the image that will be sent over the network.
